GISRasterImageConverter<T>
public class GISMappedKey<T>
extends AbstractGISRasterImageConverter<T>
implements GISRasterImageConverter<T>

A key consisting of a one-to-one map from colour to entry. The key can be added to at any time using addKey(Color, Object).

Author:
Gary Polhill
